item.title: Formula Racing Samename1
item.description: Starting the game, you immediately find yourself behind the wheel of a fast car, and there is only one thing left - to get ahead of your rivals. You will have a real race for survival. Only one will make it to the finish line. On the way to victory, all means are good, no one is going to follow the rules, and if you get in the way on the track, push your opponent to the sidelines.
